    <p>Homemade Tortilla need to be made on a flat skillet and they are cooked with much love.</p>

    <h2>Lengua</h2>
    <img src="https://imagesvc.meredithcorp.io/v3/mm/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.media-allrecipes.com%2Fuserphotos%2F2612455.jpg&w=596&h=596&c=sc&poi=face&q=85" style="width:100%">
    <p>His favorite meat inside the tortilla is Lengua which translates to cow tongue. It is usually slow cooked over many hours. Once I got over what it was and I tried it, it was very tasty.</p>

